Originally ripped by Terminal Escape, posted on April 20, 2020 Description from Terminal Escape:
This Phoenix band is just disgusting. Perhaps this is one of the many modern faces of the various and splintered subgenres that take refuge under the broad and appropriated umbrella of "power violence." Personally, I'm completely OK with that, and I'm pretty sure that BURNOUT are ok with it too. Five short minutes that will leave your day is complete shambles.  PRIMAL CODE 
https://burnout.bandcamp.com/
